Package: yarrr
Title: A companion to the e-book YaRrr!: The Pirate's Guide to R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Nathaniel", "Phillips", email = "yarrr.book@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains a mixture of functions and datasets
    referred to in the introductory e-book YaRrr!: The Pirate's Guide to
    R. The latest version of the e-book is available for free at https://
    www.thepiratesguidetor.com).
Depends: dplyr,jpeg,BayesFactor
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
URL: www.thepiratesguidetor.com
